00:16:04,408 --> 00:16:06,948
Aku akan menelepon dia dulu.

258
00:16:06,948 --> 00:16:09,548
Oke, tolong lakukan itu.

259
00:16:09,548 --> 00:16:12,887
<i>Hei, Jae Geol.</i>

260
00:16:13,558 --> 00:16:16,058
Menurutmu...

261
00:16:16,058 --> 00:16:19,127
